{"tid":1689580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 尋日嘅和理非依然太天真","createTime":"2019-11-03T01:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T03:20:58.000Z","uid":23573,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"30433749629e66e98f89303218cdc4b07eb851d2","tid":1689580,"uid":23573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:33:08.000Z","msg":"我唔係指打黑警、放哨之類，呢樣已經好多人講過<br />\n而係我睇到下面呢條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yanwu0701/videos/765661813904379/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyanwu0701%2Fvideos%2F765661813904379%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=cc1302e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yanwu0701/videos/765661813904379/</a><br />\n<br />\n百幾個係修頓被拉和理非<br />\n旁邊嘅人已經叫到失聲咁滯<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係無幾個和理非識得望鏡頭</span><br />\n對比前線手足已經識大叫自己名、望鏡頭<br />\n和理非依然缺乏警覺性<br />\n<br />\n今時今日嘅黑警係咩都做得出<br />\n「和理非」已經唔係免死金牌<br />\n唔一定代表黑警拉左你返去唔會搞你<br />\n<br />\n被拉之後，請記得：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">吸引記者鏡頭注意、望鏡頭、大叫自己個名</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ce3fef5e6d7755fab9131342c2459b36f76f2308","tid":1689580,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e868f05ce75b9de0da7450c65da5ea747ea8e423","tid":1689580,"uid":23573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:35:40.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7291476392f0875ed1678d2bebe5f276cbc9c57d","tid":1689580,"uid":278313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:39:23.000Z","msg":"敢肯定未出嚟之前有俾啲object威脅過唔準出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部一粒聲都唔敢出 前一批仲